        "Length",
        "Checksum",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。UDP头部固定是8字节对吧？那源端口和目的端口各占2字节，长度和校验和各2字节。后面的Data字段长度不固定，这次我们假设是4字节，用来存物流仓储的标识信息？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Length",
        "Checksum",
        "Data"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的，头部8字节。Data部分我们用4字节，标注为Logistics_Warehouse，表示这是物流仓储的专用数据区。整个包从第0位到第95位，一共12字节。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data (Logistics_Warehouse)",
        "0-95"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画一版：0-15位是Source Port，16-31位是Destination Port，32-47位是Length，48-63位是Checksum，64-95位是Data。您看看字段命名和位宽有没有问题？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "0-15",
        "16-31",
        "32-47",
        "48-63",
        "64-95"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "位宽都对，但Data字段的标注需要调整。不能直接写Data，要明确写上Logistics_Warehouse，不然同事会误解成普通数据区。改成\"Data (Logistics_Warehouse)\"吧。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Data (Logistics_Warehouse)"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，Data字段现在显示为\"Data (Logistics_Warehouse)\"。另外我在图上方加了个标题\"Estructura del paquete UDP\"，因为是给海外仓库团队看的文档。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "Data (Logistics_Warehouse)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "标题用西班牙语没问题。再确认一下：Source Port和Destination Port都是16位宽，Length和Checksum也是16位，最后Data是32位。总长度96位，没错吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Source Port",
        "Destination Port",
        "Length",
        "Checksum",
        "Data (Logistics_Warehouse)"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
